title: 240: 10 Takeaways from Week 13
itunes:title: 240: 10 Takeaways from Week 13
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks recap the biggest games around the league from week 13. Is Derrick Henry finally a number one running back (4:05)? Does Todd Bowles deserve the coach of the year award (11:49)? Can Russell Wilson continue his MVP push (26:21)? All that and much more on this edition of Move the Sticks presented by the Ford F-Series.
